{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/avengers-my-hero-academia-crossover/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Kolaborasi Avengers dan My Hero Academia Adalah Crossover Superhero Paling Ambisius","content":"<p>Di bulan April ini, <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengupas-trailer-official-avengers-infinity-war-lebih-dalam/\">Avengers: Infinity War</a> akan segera tayang. Banyak orang menyebut film ketiga Avengers ini sebagai film <em>crossover</em> paling ambisius yang pernah ada. Hmm, benarkah begitu? Bagaimana jika kumpulan <em>superhero</em> asal Amerika ini bertemu dengan kumpulan <em>superhero</em> asal Jepang?</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/8-vkFY5s7FQ\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Jawabannya adalah sebuah kolaborasi antara film Avengers: Infinity War dan <em>anime</em> My Hero Academia. Keduanya menampilkan puluhan karakter <em>superhero</em> dengan berbagai kemampuan unik. Dan saat keduanya saling bertemu, <em>crossover</em> paling ambisius dan paling besar pun lahir. Tujuannya apa lagi kalau bukan mempromosikan film Infinity War dan <em>anime</em> <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/anime-spring-2018-baru/\">My hero Academia</a> <em>season</em> ketiga.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45862\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45862\" data-attachment-id=\"45862\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/avengers-my-hero-academia-crossover/attachment/01-avengers-mha/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-avengers-mha.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-avengers-mha\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-avengers-mha.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45862\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-avengers-mha.jpg\" alt=\"01-avengers-mha\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-avengers-mha.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/01-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45862\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Nerdist</p></div></p>\n<p>Buat kamu yang belum tahu, My Hero Academia adalah serial <em>manga</em> dan <em>anime</em> dengan tema aksi <em>superhero</em>. Diceritakan bahwa 80% penduduk bumi kini memiliki kekuatan super yang disebut dengan Quirk. Karakter utama Izuku Midoriya adalah satu dari 20% sisanya yang tidak memiliki Quirk. Ia kemudian bertemu dengan <em>superhero</em> All Might yang memberikan Izuku Quirk unik yang bisa diwariskan. Dengan kekuatan barunya, Izuku masuk ke sekolah UA High untuk membuktikan kemampuannya.</p>\n<p>Kembali ke topik kolaborasi antara Avengers dan My Hero Academia, ternyata ada cerita di balik event tersebut. Cerita tersebut dituturkan lewat beberapa episode pendek yang terbit di Youtube. Premisnya cukup sederhana, dimana All Might bertanya kepada Izuku dan teman-teman tentang siapa sosok Avengers idola mereka.</p>\n<p>Satu per satu, Izuku dan teman-teman menceritakan superhero idola mereka. Ternyata ada kesamaan antara diri mereka dengan <em>superhero</em> favorit masing-masing! Penasaran siapa yang jadi favorit siapa? Yuk disimak satu per satu!</p>\n<h1>Izuku Midoriya Mengidolakan Captain America!</h1>\n<p><iframe src=\" https://www.youtube.com/embed/f623A5vBWr4\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Menurut Izuku, Avengers idolanya adalah Captain America. Ternyata ada banyak kesamaan antara Izuku dan sosok pemimpin alami Avengers tersebut. Di masa lalu, keduanya memiliki tubuh yang lemah, sehingga sering kali ditindas. Meski begitu, keduanya memiliki jiwa kepahlawanan dan kebajikan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45863\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45863\" data-attachment-id=\"45863\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/avengers-my-hero-academia-crossover/attachment/02-avengers-mha/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-avengers-mha.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-avengers-mha\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-avengers-mha.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45863\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-avengers-mha.jpg\" alt=\"02-avengers-mha\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-avengers-mha.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/02-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45863\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: My Hero Academia</p></div></p>\n<p>Keteguhan hati dan sifat welas asih mereka kemudian membuat keduanya mendapatkan kekuatan super. Jika Izuku mendapatkan kekuatannya dari All Might, maka Captain America mendapatkannya dari serum super.</p>\n<h1>Katsuki Bakugo Mengidolakan Iron Man!</h1>\n<p><iframe src=\" https://www.youtube.com/embed/_-bvCuqrep8\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Teman dan rival Izuku, Katsuki, ternyata mengidolakan Iron Man. Katsuki memang tidak sekaya dan sejenius Tony Stark, namun keduanya sama-sama punya sifat angkuh dan arogan. Meski demikian, mereka adalah sosok setia kawan yang bisa diandalkan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45864\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45864\" data-attachment-id=\"45864\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/avengers-my-hero-academia-crossover/attachment/03-avengers-mha/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-avengers-mha.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-avengers-mha\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-avengers-mha.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45864\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-avengers-mha.jpg\" alt=\"03 avengers my hero academia\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-avengers-mha.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/03-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45864\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: My Hero Academia</p></div></p>\n<p>Katsuki juga tidak bertarung menggunakan <em>armor</em> berteknologi tinggi. Namun baik Katsuki dan Iron Man bisa mengeluarkan ledakan dari telapak tangan mereka.</p>\n<h1>Ochako Uraraka Mengidolakan Black Widow!</h1>\n<p><iframe src=\" https://www.youtube.com/embed/R0umsBa5bd0\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Sementara itu teman dekat Izuku, Ochako, mengidolakan Black Widow. Keduanya adalah karakter tipe <em>action girl</em> yang bisa bertarung.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45865\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45865\" data-attachment-id=\"45865\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/avengers-my-hero-academia-crossover/attachment/04-avengers-mha/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-avengers-mha.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-avengers-mha\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-avengers-mha.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45865\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-avengers-mha.jpg\" alt=\"04-avengers-mha\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-avengers-mha.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/04-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45865\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: My Hero Academia</p></div></p>\n<p>Meski Black Widow dan Ochako tidak punya kekuatan super sekeren teman-teman mereka, namun keduanya memiliki kemampuan fisik di atas rata-rata, atau bahkan setara dengan para <em>superhero</em> laki-laki lainnya.</p>\n<h1>Tenya Iida Mengidolakan Doctor Strange!</h1>\n<p><iframe src=\" https://www.youtube.com/embed/z4cd68-fwTA\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Ketua kelas 1A, Tenya, mengidolakan Doctor Strange. Quirk milik Tenya sendiri bukan berjenis sihir, melainkan kecepatan super. Meski demikian, ambisi Tenya menjadi seorang <em>superhero</em> terbaik sejalan dengan ambisi Stephen Strange untuk menjadi dokter dan penyihir terbaik.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45866\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45866\" data-attachment-id=\"45866\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/avengers-my-hero-academia-crossover/attachment/05-avengers-mha/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-avengers-mha.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-avengers-mha\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-avengers-mha.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45866\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-avengers-mha.jpg\" alt=\"05-avengers-mha\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-avengers-mha.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/05-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45866\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: My Hero Academia</p></div></p>\n<p>Pun sebagai ketua kelas, Tenya adalah sosok yang sangat rajin, layaknya Strange yang juga terobsesi mendalami pengetahuan sihir.</p>\n<h1>Shoto Todoroki Mengidolakan Thor!</h1>\n<p><iframe src=\" https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ogm5yASvrnc\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Siswa UA Academy yang masuk lewat jalur beasiswa, Shoto, mengidolakan Thor. Keduanya memiliki kekuatan elemen, dimana Thor mengendalikan elemen petir sementara Shoto mengendalikan api dan es.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45867\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45867\" data-attachment-id=\"45867\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/avengers-my-hero-academia-crossover/attachment/06-avengers-mha/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/06-avengers-mha.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-avengers-mha\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/06-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/06-avengers-mha.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45867\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/06-avengers-mha.jpg\" alt=\"06-avengers-mha\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/06-avengers-mha.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/06-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45867\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: My Hero Academia</p></div></p>\n<p>Baik Shoto dan Thor memiliki kepribadian yang mudah berubah. Shoto bisa menjadi sosok yang cool dan berapi-api tergantung keadaan. Sementara itu, Thor yang berasal dari Asgard memiliki jiwa ksatria dan tegas. Setelah menghabiskan waktunya di bumi, Thor pun menjadi orang yang lebih luwes dan senang berkelakar.</p>\n<h1>All Might Mengidolakan Hulk?!</h1>\n<p><iframe src=\" https://www.youtube.com/embed/3wKucNCbivM\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Sosok <em>superhero</em> terhebat All Might juga punya Avengers yang ia idolakan. Apakah dia Captain America layaknya Izuku? Ternyata All Might mengidolakan Hulk! Kok bisa?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_45868\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-45868\" data-attachment-id=\"45868\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/avengers-my-hero-academia-crossover/attachment/07-avengers-mha/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/07-avengers-mha.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-avengers-mha\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/07-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/07-avengers-mha.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-45868\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/07-avengers-mha.jpg\" alt=\"07-avengers-mha\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/07-avengers-mha.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/07-avengers-mha-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-45868\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: My Hero Academia</p></div></p>\n<p>All Might ternyata bercermin pada sosok dirinya sendiri saat melihat Hulk. Dalam wujud normalnya, baik All Might dan Bruce Banner memiliki tubuh yang ringkih dan tak bertenaga. Namun dengan kekuatan super mereka, keduanya bisa berubah menjadi sosok yang jauh lebih kuat untuk membela kebenaran.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Nah, barusan adalah para <em>superhero</em> Avengers idola karakter My Hero Academia. Menurut kamu, ada lagi nggak karakter Avengers yang mirip dengan karakter My Hero Academia? Siapa <em>pairing</em> karakter favorit kamu dari lima pasangan di atas? Tulis di kolom komentar ya!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"527e7502-f10a-531c-b817-e6a043983e3b"}}}